title: SleepPhones Classic
description:
SleepPhones® Classic provides superior sound quality with eco-friendly, lead-free electronics.  They feature a four-foot braided fabric cord and are compatible with any device with a standard 3.5 mm audio jack.  The speakers inside are fully adjustable to suit your unique head shape.

Questions?  Please contact our Customer Service Representatives at Service@AcousticSheep.com or call 877-838-4790.  Happy Sleeping!
